到受騷擾只是主觀感覺，未必來自同一隻狗，形容被告行為殘忍、滅絕人性，而且非一時衝動。鑑於加上近期較多虐待動物的個案，必須判處具阻嚇性刑罰，遂判監禁八個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殺隻狗都坐8個月"},{"pid":"c23ea6b04514d575346fd7e620d2328c504df080","tid":472288,"uid":693,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法官昨判刑前特意觀看事發時的閉路電視片段，認為小販當時只是想離開，並非故意傷人，亦無過度用力，相信結果無人能料，故輕判監禁1年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坐一年，殺隻狗都唔止啦</blockquote><br />\n食環咪係狗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b10e7c801f8b845e7cc2b775c5d7fd5cd78477","tid":472288,"uid":40588,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:02:08.000Z","msg":"食環大戰蝻 <br />\n<br />\n難分難解"},{"pid":"b623562308ec577c670cc14f895aa323be60ea99","tid":472288,"uid":16567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法官昨判刑前特意觀看事發時的閉路電視片段，認為小販當時只是想離開，並非故意傷人，亦無過度用力，相信結果無人能料，故輕判監禁1年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坐一年，殺隻狗都唔止啦</blockquote><br />\n食環咪係狗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比隻狗咬仲要判坐監"},{"pid":"4f0ee318ad85c6111d3ecafe0c574c7989ec8c36","tid":472288,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:12:17.000Z","msg":"食環狗要佗槍會點？"},{"pid":"adf1c5f2c7c3ebca4bf138cae6eb005690733c93","tid":472288,"uid":55488,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"716d6ed2b22ea123df05e77b2d56cab5c8819dcb","tid":472288,"uid":26976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:22:58.000Z","msg":"由阿婆升級打蝻<br />\n都未升夠lv抵輸啦"},{"pid":"f6d878275dd587c617957874bb44a94a803dce59","tid":472288,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"無記錯<br />\n平時兩個人行咇<br />\n廢老懶醒單拖捉人<br />\n唔跟規舉 搞出事<br />\n隻鑊邊個揹"},{"pid":"e26022d70fe43c1a6b64f11be7a5b9b8f7fde09a","tid":4